								</span>
								<div
									class='w-20 bg-gray-200 rounded-sketch h-2'>
									<div
										class='bg-orange-600 h-full rounded-sketch'
										style='width: 95%'
									></div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class='flex items-center justify-between'>
								<span class='flex items-center gap-2'>
									<span class='text-blue-600'>⚛️</span>
									<span class='font-medium'>React</span>
								</span>
								<div
									class='w-20 bg-gray-200 rounded-sketch h-2'>
									<div
										class='bg-blue-600 h-full rounded-sketch'
										style='width: 70%'
									></div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class='flex items-center justify-between'>
								<span class='flex items-center gap-2'>
									<span class='text-green-600'>🟢</span>
									<span class='font-medium'>Node.js</span>
								</span>
								<div
									class='w-20 bg-gray-200 rounded-sketch h-2'>
									<div
										class='bg-green-600 h-full rounded-sketch'
										style='width: 75%'
									></div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class='flex items-center justify-between'>
								<span class='flex items-center gap-2'>
									<span class='text-indigo-600'>💾</span>
									<span class='font-medium'>MySQL</span>
								</span>
								<div
									class='w-20 bg-gray-200 rounded-sketch h-2'>
									<div
										class='bg-indigo-600 h-full rounded-sketch'
										style='width: 85%'
									></div>
