								</span>
								<div
									class='w-20 bg-gray-200 rounded-sketch h-2'>
									<div
										class='bg-blue-400 h-full rounded-sketch'
										style='width: 95%'
									></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Habilidades de Diseño -->
				<div class='card-sketch'>
					<div
						class='bg-white/90 dark:bg-gray-800/90 border-4 border-pink-300 dark:border-pink-600 rounded-sketch-lg p-6 shadow-sketch'>
						<div class='text-center mb-6'>
							<div class='text-4xl mb-3'>🎨</div>
